{"snp4.11:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 4.11 ","snp4.11:0.2":"Kalahavivadasutta ","snp4.11:1.1":"“Kutopahuta kalaha vivada, ","snp4.11:1.2":"Paridevasoka sahamacchara ca; ","snp4.11:1.3":"Manatimana sahapesuna ca, ","snp4.11:1.4":"Kutopahuta te tadingha bruhi”. ","snp4.11:2.1":"“Piyappahuta kalaha vivada, ","snp4.11:2.2":"Paridevasoka sahamacchara ca; ","snp4.11:2.3":"Manatimana sahapesuna ca, ","snp4.11:2.4":"Maccherayutta kalaha vivada; ","snp4.11:2.5":"Vivadajatesu ca pesunani”. ","snp4.11:3.1":"“Piya su lokasmim kutonidana, ","snp4.11:3.2":"Ye capi lobha vicaranti loke; ","snp4.11:3.3":"Asa ca nittha ca kutonidana, ","snp4.11:3.4":"Ye samparayaya narassa honti”. ","snp4.11:4.1":"“Chandanidanani piyani loke, ","snp4.11:4.2":"Ye capi lobha vicaranti loke; ","snp4.11:4.3":"Asa ca nittha ca itonidana, ","snp4.11:4.4":"Ye samparayaya narassa honti”. ","snp4.11:5.1":"“Chando nu lokasmim kutonidano, ","snp4.11:5.2":"Vinicchaya capi kutopahuta; ","snp4.11:5.3":"Kodho mosavajjanca kathankatha ca, ","snp4.11:5.4":"Ye vapi dhamma samanena vutta”. ","snp4.11:6.1":"“Satam asatanti yamahu loke, ","snp4.11:6.2":"Tamupanissaya pahoti chando; ","snp4.11:6.3":"Rupesu disva vibhavam bhavanca, ","snp4.11:6.4":"Vinicchayam kubbati jantu loke. ","snp4.11:7.1":"Kodho mosavajjanca kathankatha ca, ","snp4.11:7.2":"Etepi dhamma dvayameva sante; ","snp4.11:7.3":"Kathankathi nanapathaya sikkhe, ","snp4.11:7.4":"Natva pavutta samanena dhamma”. ","snp4.11:8.1":"“Satam asatanca kutonidana, ","snp4.11:8.2":"Kismim asante na bhavanti hete; ","snp4.11:8.3":"Vibhavam bhavancapi yametamattham, ","snp4.11:8.4":"Etam me pabruhi yatonidanam”. ","snp4.11:9.1":"“Phassanidanam satam asatam, ","snp4.11:9.2":"Phasse asante na bhavanti hete; ","snp4.11:9.3":"Vibhavam bhavancapi yametamattham, ","snp4.11:9.4":"Etam te pabrumi itonidanam”. ","snp4.11:10.1":"“Phasso nu lokasmi kutonidano, ","snp4.11:10.2":"Pariggaha capi kutopahuta; ","snp4.11:10.3":"Kismim asante na mamattamatthi, ","snp4.11:10.4":"Kismim vibhute na phusanti phassa”. ","snp4.11:11.1":"“Namanca rupanca paticca phasso, ","snp4.11:11.2":"Icchanidanani pariggahani; ","snp4.11:11.3":"Icchayasantya na mamattamatthi, ","snp4.11:11.4":"Rupe vibhute na phusanti phassa”. ","snp4.11:12.1":"“Katham sametassa vibhoti rupam, ","snp4.11:12.2":"Sukham dukhancapi katham vibhoti; ","snp4.11:12.3":"Etam me pabruhi yatha vibhoti, ","snp4.11:12.4":"Tam janiyamati me mano ahu”. ","snp4.11:13.1":"“Na sannasanni na visannasanni, ","snp4.11:13.2":"Nopi asanni na vibhutasanni; ","snp4.11:13.3":"Evam sametassa vibhoti rupam, ","snp4.11:13.4":"Sannanidana hi papancasankha”. ","snp4.11:14.1":"“Yam tam apucchimha akittayi no, ","snp4.11:14.2":"Annam tam pucchama tadingha bruhi; ","snp4.11:14.3":"Ettavataggam nu vadanti heke, ","snp4.11:14.4":"Yakkhassa suddhim idha panditase; ","snp4.11:14.5":"Udahu annampi vadanti etto”. ","snp4.11:15.1":"“Ettavataggampi vadanti heke, ","snp4.11:15.2":"Yakkhassa suddhim idha panditase; ","snp4.11:15.3":"Tesam paneke samayam vadanti, ","snp4.11:15.4":"Anupadisese kusala vadana. ","snp4.11:16.1":"Ete ca natva upanissitati, ","snp4.11:16.2":"Natva muni nissaye so vimamsi; ","snp4.11:16.3":"Natva vimutto na vivadameti, ","snp4.11:16.4":"Bhavabhavaya na sameti dhiro”ti. ","snp4.11:16.5":"Kalahavivadasuttam ekadasamam. "}